Start
/ Narrow — %config!file!path% resolves whether config narrowed to dict or not.
/ Chain-wide !, never headline-only — no flow-dependent crash on the un-examined branch.
- save 'narrowchain.json' with content '{"db":"plang"}'
/ un-examined branch: the file facet answers from the headline
- read file 'narrowchain.json', write to %config%
- set %loc1% = %config!file!path%
- assert %loc1% is not null
- assert %config% is file
/ examine the content → narrows to dict, file retained in the chain
- set %db% = %config.db%
- assert %db% equals "plang"
- assert %config% is dict
- assert %config% is file
/ post-narrow: the SAME facet hop still resolves
- set %loc2% = %config!file!path%
- assert %loc2% is not null
- delete file 'narrowchain.json'
